  <li>ISO 9241-143: Forms (2012)</li>
  <li><a href="https://www.nngroup.com/articles/radio-buttons-default-selection/" class="icon-link">Kara Pernice: Radio Buttons: Select One by Default or Leave All Unselected? (2014)<svg class="icon-svg" focusable="false" aria-hidden="true"><use xlink:href="#open-in-new"></use></svg></a></li>
  <li><a href="https://www.nngroup.com/articles/checkboxes-vs-radio-buttons/" class="icon-link">Jakob Nielsen: Checkboxes vs. Radio Buttons (2004)<svg class="icon-svg" focusable="false" aria-hidden="true"><use xlink:href="#open-in-new"></use></svg></a></li>
</ul>

